- Admits pleasing fans is almost impossible

## Movie-making AI and broken story

- Prompt-based system keeps expanding script to 3,000+ pages
- No antagonist/third act means characters trapped in movie

## Fixing the franchise ending
- Plan: restore cut material, revive Baron/Tannenbaum storyline
- New plan: jailbreak Tannenbaum, reunite with Robotrees, kill him
- Machine finally recognizes this as a proper ending

## Industry satire and Snyder cameo

- Gunn worries about losing touch with audiences

## Evil plan, Samantha, and world-saving
